---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Worflo — Debug & Monitor HubSpot Workflows">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Built for HubSpot Operations Teams</span>
      <h1>Stop guessing why your<br/><span>HubSpot workflows break</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Execution tracking, version control, pre-flight checks, branch coverage, duplicate detection, and one-click rollback — everything HubSpot's native tools don't give you.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="https://app.worflo.io/connect" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Connect HubSpot — it's free →</a>
        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">See how it works</a>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-proof">
        <span>No credit card required · Free for up to 3 workflows · Installs in 60 seconds</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- App screenshot mockup -->
  <section class="screenshot-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="screenshot-wrap">
        <div class="screenshot-bar">
          <span class="screenshot-dot" style="background:#ff5f57"></span>
          <span class="screenshot-dot" style="background:#febc2e"></span>
          <span class="screenshot-dot" style="background:#28c840"></span>
          <span class="screenshot-url">app.worflo.io/workflows/142</span>
        </div>
        <div class="screenshot-placeholder">
          <div class="screenshot-ui">
            <div class="ui-sidebar">
              <div class="ui-sidebar-item">▦ Dashboard</div>
              <div class="ui-sidebar-item active">⎇ Workflows</div>
              <div class="ui-sidebar-item">🔍 Search</div>
              <div class="ui-sidebar-item">✦ Insights</div>
              <div class="ui-sidebar-item">🗺️ Dep Map</div>
              <div class="ui-sidebar-item">🔔 Alerts</div>
              <div class="ui-sidebar-item" style="margin-top:auto">⚙ Settings</div>
            </div>
            <div class="ui-main">
              <div class="ui-header">
                <span class="ui-title">Lead Nurture Sequence</span>
                <div style="display:flex;gap:6px">
                  <span class="ui-badge green">Active</span>
                  <span class="ui-badge blue">v4 · Latest</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ui-rows">
                <div class="ui-row">
                  <span class="ui-badge green">✓</span>
                  <span class="ui-row-name">Contact enrolled — ACME Corp</span>
                  <span class="ui-row-meta">8 steps · 1.2s</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ui-row" style="border-left:3px solid #de350b">
                  <span class="ui-badge red">✗</span>
                  <span class="ui-row-name">Webhook failed — timeout</span>
                  <span class="ui-row-meta" style="color:#de350b">Step 4 · 2m ago</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ui-row">
                  <span class="ui-badge green">✓</span>
                  <span class="ui-row-name">Email sent — john@example.com</span>
                  <span class="ui-row-meta">6 steps · 0.8s</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ui-row">
                  <span class="ui-badge green">✓</span>
                  <span class="ui-row-name">Property updated — Deal Stage</span>
                  <span class="ui-row-meta">3 steps · 0.3s</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section class="problem">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>HubSpot workflows fail silently.</h2>
      <p class="problem-sub">HubSpot gives you a green tick or a vague error. Nothing else. When something breaks, you're left guessing.</p>
      <div class="problem-grid">
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">🔇</div>
          <h3>Silent failures</h3>
          <p>Workflows error without alerting anyone. Contacts fall through the cracks and you find out days later — from a customer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">⏪</div>
          <h3>No version history</h3>
          <p>Someone changed the workflow. You don't know who, what they changed, or when. There's no undo. HubSpot's native revert excludes custom code and webhooks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">🌀</div>
          <h3>Can't test safely</h3>
          <p>Testing means enrolling real contacts. There's no staging environment, no dry run, no way to see what will happen before it does.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features -->
  <section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Features</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything your ops team needs</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Built specifically for the gaps HubSpot's native tooling leaves open.</p>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔬</div>
          <h3>Execution Trace Inspector</h3>
          <p>See every step of every workflow run — inputs, outputs, timing, and errors. Click into any trace to see exactly where it failed and why.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">⎇</div>
          <h3>Full Version History</h3>
          <p>Every change to your workflow is captured automatically. Compare any two versions with a line-by-line diff, including custom code and webhook configs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">↩</div>
          <h3>One-Click Rollback</h3>
          <p>Restore any previous version in seconds. Worflo pushes the change directly to HubSpot via API — no manual reconstruction required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">✈</div>
          <h3>Pre-Flight Inspector</h3>
          <p>Scan any workflow for configuration issues before they cause problems — broken webhook URLs, empty conditions, re-enrollment loops, and more. Scored 0–100.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
          <h3>Error Pattern Detection</h3>
          <p>Automatically groups repeated failures by step type and error message. Find systemic issues before they affect hundreds of contacts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">⎇</div>
          <h3>Branch Coverage</h3>
          <p>See which conditional branches in your workflows are actually being taken — and which are dead ends that have never fired in 30 days.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">✨</div>
          <h3>AI-Powered Diff Summaries</h3>
          <p>Plain-English explanations of what changed between workflow versions. No more decoding JSON to understand what your colleague updated.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔔</div>
          <h3>Instant Alerts + Spike Detection</h3>
          <p>Alerts the moment a workflow errors. Enrollment spike detection fires when a workflow suddenly enrolls 5× its normal rate — catch re-enrollment loops before they spiral.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">💰</div>
          <h3>API Cost Estimator</h3>
          <p>See how many HubSpot API calls each workflow burns per execution. Project monthly usage against rate limits and get recommendations to reduce overhead.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🗺️</div>
          <h3>Dependency Map</h3>
          <p>Visualise which workflows share lists, webhooks, or action types. Know the blast radius before you change anything.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">✦</div>
          <h3>Insights Dashboard</h3>
          <p>Duplicate workflow detection, property usage auditing, deal stage coverage gaps, and form-to-workflow dependency mapping — all in one place.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🏢</div>
          <h3>Multi-Portal Support</h3>
          <p>Manage workflows across multiple HubSpot portals from a single Worflo account. Built for agencies and enterprise teams.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How it works -->
  <section class="how">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">How it works</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Up and running in 60 seconds</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">No code, no configuration, no HubSpot developer access required.</p>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3>Connect HubSpot</h3>
          <p>Authorise Worflo via HubSpot OAuth. We request read-only access by default. No HubSpot admin required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3>Workflows sync automatically</h3>
          <p>Worflo pulls your workflows, captures version snapshots, and starts logging execution traces within minutes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3>Debug with confidence</h3>
          <p>Inspect failures, compare versions, set up alerts, and roll back when something goes wrong — all from one dashboard.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="pricing" id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Pricing</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Simple, transparent pricing</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Start free. Upgrade as your team grows. All prices in USD.</p>

      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <div class="pricing-name">Free</div>
          <div class="pricing-price">$0</div>
          <div class="pricing-period">forever</div>
          <p class="pricing-desc">Try Worflo with your 3 most important workflows.</p>
          <hr class="pricing-divider" />
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>3 workflows</li>
            <li>7-day trace history</li>
            <li>Version history</li>
            <li>Diff viewer</li>
            <li>Email alerts</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://app.worflo.io/connect" class="btn btn-outline pricing-cta">Get started free</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card featured">
          <div class="pricing-badge">Most popular</div>
          <div class="pricing-name">Pro</div>
          <div class="pricing-price"><sup>$</sup>49</div>
          <div class="pricing-period">per month</div>
          <p class="pricing-desc">For growing teams who rely on HubSpot workflows daily.</p>
          <hr class="pricing-divider" />
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Unlimited workflows</li>
            <li>90-day trace history</li>
            <li>Execution tracking</li>
            <li>Pre-Flight Inspector</li>
            <li>Branch coverage</li>
            <li>API cost estimator</li>
            <li>Enrollment spike alerts</li>
            <li>AI diff summaries</li>
            <li>One-click rollback</li>
            <li>Error pattern detection</li>
            <li>Slack + webhook alerts</li>
            <li>CSV export</li>
            <li>Up to 5 team members</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://app.worflo.io/connect" class="btn btn-primary pricing-cta">Start Pro trial</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card">
          <div class="pricing-name">Agency</div>
          <div class="pricing-price"><sup>$</sup>149</div>
          <div class="pricing-period">per month</div>
          <p class="pricing-desc">For agencies managing workflows across multiple client portals.</p>
          <hr class="pricing-divider" />
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Pro</li>
            <li>Multiple HubSpot portals</li>
            <li>Insights dashboard</li>
            <li>Duplicate workflow detector</li>
            <li>Property usage auditor</li>
            <li>Deal stage coverage map</li>
            <li>Form dependency map</li>
            <li>Dependency map</li>
            <li>Workflow simulation</li>
            <li>Unlimited team members</li>
            <li>Priority support</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://app.worflo.io/connect" class="btn btn-outline pricing-cta">Start Agency trial</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card">
          <div class="pricing-name">Enterprise</div>
          <div class="pricing-price"><sup>$</sup>299</div>
          <div class="pricing-period">per month</div>
          <p class="pricing-desc">For large teams needing dedicated support and custom integrations.</p>
          <hr class="pricing-divider" />
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Agency</li>
            <li>Unlimited portals</li>
            <li>Dedicated onboarding</li>
            <li>SLA + uptime guarantee</li>
            <li>Custom integrations</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="mailto:hello@worflo.io" class="btn btn-outline pricing-cta">Contact us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">FAQ</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Common questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Does Worflo modify my HubSpot workflows?</h3>
          <p>Only when you ask it to. Rollback and execution tracking both require explicit confirmation. When you enable tracking, Worflo adds a single silent webhook step labelled "Worflo Execution Tracking" — you can remove it at any time. Everything else is read-only.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How are execution traces captured?</h3>
          <p>When you enable tracking on a workflow, Worflo injects a silent webhook step as the first action. Every time that workflow runs, HubSpot fires the webhook and Worflo records the execution. There's no polling lag — traces appear in seconds. You can enable tracking on all workflows at once from the Workflows page.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Will this work with my existing HubSpot plan?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Worflo works with HubSpot Professional and Enterprise plans (Workflows is not available on Starter). It connects via standard OAuth — no developer account required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How long is trace data retained?</h3>
          <p>7 days on Free, 90 days on Pro and above.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is my HubSpot data secure?</h3>
          <p>Yes. OAuth tokens are encrypted at rest. We never store contact PII — traces contain only object IDs and workflow execution metadata. Data is hosted on AWS in Sydney.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I cancel anytime?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Cancel from the billing page at any time. Your subscription stays active until the end of the billing period, then reverts to the Free plan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA band -->
  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Start debugging in 60 seconds</h2>
      <p>Free forever for up to 3 workflows. No credit card required.</p>
      <a href="https://app.worflo.io/connect" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">Connect HubSpot →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
